                "questionText": "1. Cho hình vẽ bên, biết: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/886e71f7-be62-4c74-82c5-81e9aa44bf84.png\"/> <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/b00feb5e-6c37-4e0e-9131-370d1817bcf0.png\"/> <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/fec1d60b-703b-4843-8f34-018afc9093f1.png\"/> Tính chiều cao <i>AB</i> của cây (kết quả làm tròn đến mét).<br><img src=\"https://asset.moon.vn/img/chat/large/2026/1/6f73b7c3-ee46-4c4e-ae56-96af2e382ec6.jpg\" data-filename=\"\" style=\"max-width: 600px; height: auto;\"><br>2. Cho tam giác <i>ABC</i> nhọn <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/1ad25bcd-5d17-4638-88f9-23703bcb1691.png\"/> đường cao AH <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/17ddcbc4-771d-4f09-99e9-01defed27cc7.png\"/> Đường phân giác của <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/edacfa5b-6590-431c-a288-d73c709db321.png\"/> cắt <i>BC</i> tại <i>D</i>. Gọi <i>E, F</i> lần lượt là chân đường vuông góc kẻ từ <i>D</i> tới <i>AB, AC</i>.\n<br>a) Chứng minh \n<br>b) Tia <i>FE</i> cắt <i>AD</i> tại <i>K</i>. Chứng minh <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/75069481-efb3-4401-bac7-43993488acd1.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/daa3fdd1-f4fe-478e-be46-83f06305a099.png\"/>\n<br>c) Đường thẳng đi qua <i>D</i> vuông góc với <i>BC</i>, cắt <i>EF</i> tại <i>J</i>. Chứng minh <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/9780c850-c0fe-4267-8b60-f4017a99d402.png\"/>\n",
                "answer": "1)<img src=\"https://asset.moon.vn/img/chat/large/2026/1/3a72e03d-cf3b-45b0-baae-7484f609a753.jpg\" data-filename=\"\" style=\"max-width: 600px; height: auto;\"><br>Xét <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/f260ee76-65a5-4061-8b18-7e4243b38988.png\"/> có\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/abfa36b8-e965-48c2-b0d1-8d4398ff3f03.png\"/> <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/7b7c5fa1-222a-49ea-ae5d-f4b048af52ee.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/c57e9754-b1d3-4904-81bc-63a4e3dba09b.png\"/> (hệ quả định lý Thales)\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/0e063c1b-914d-4157-a710-f611e894d21b.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/1b158679-5d3c-4bb4-bd8b-c661fd37a8f0.png\"/>\n<br>Vậy chiều cao của cây khoảng 8 m.\n<br>2a)<img src=\"https://asset.moon.vn/img/chat/large/2026/1/b53cea0f-348e-47e8-b369-52c3e0433524.jpg\" data-filename=\"\" style=\"max-width: 600px; height: auto;\"><br>Xét <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/ec07c95f-846f-4148-af3f-ab4320d7ac9d.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/a4f71477-f465-4989-b18b-1f07b6a5a88a.png\"/> có:\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/f3ffe700-fd5f-4e36-abf2-67092217f0c0.png\"/> chung\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/cde1d054-31a4-4efe-a75f-feb5c7bb5fa1.png\"/>\n<br>Suy ra \n<br>2b) Ta có: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/42ce5593-7992-4280-a365-b9d11d9f1cdf.png\"/> (tỉ số đồng dạng)\n<br>Ta có: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/3e5b5020-ab11-4adb-9d3d-3e53f023dc75.png\"/> <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/de0875eb-0a2e-4dc3-9fc3-7058a5e5778c.png\"/> <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/1a7cab74-0c39-4790-906b-783981ab9f57.png\"/> <i>AD</i> chung\n<br>Suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/bf048cc9-61bd-4e49-9331-a522f8a30181.png\"/> <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/96eb55b4-72bc-419a-bcef-7f7dc58a3204.png\"/> Suy ra <i>AD</i> là đường trung trực của <i>EF</i>.\n<br>Suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/2ec2cbfe-d93b-47b0-b0cf-6bd45ef0d403.png\"/>\n<br>Suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/75ed6f54-9e94-4646-9ac1-d1d91e0d2161.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/b88e0f27-3ee5-4d72-a9dd-83360774ec03.png\"/> (cùng phụ <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/70246ec6-0330-4557-9d82-43f8b5bb16a7.png\"/>)\n<br>Mặt khác <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/c78aeec6-a195-40b3-9bb6-49d94ec250ca.png\"/> Suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/230df0b8-5b70-4d5f-bc56-c0c84bf56bee.png\"/>\n<br>2c) Xét <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/28fb8725-50fc-4035-92a0-bd820e3c8a82.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/2bfae3d4-2ae3-41bc-b33d-3b7b8857eba4.png\"/> có: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/14efd03a-2cd4-49c0-a4d3-e5a53d403338.png\"/> (cmt); <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/0e86e514-0a2c-427a-a91d-cfe1d22b25fd.png\"/> (cùng phụ <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/9a7cc25d-8a9a-4a33-8f79-ff4ca343637f.png\"/>)\n<br>Suy ra  Suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/785701a8-a657-44bb-9de5-006c6e70d6e5.png\"/> (1)\n<br>Xét <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/9212de76-423e-4da9-892d-130f03dd5170.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/a06287d0-fb55-44d9-accc-3e08ae6661f4.png\"/> có: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/a5ea722d-59f7-4977-a418-303c43b632b6.png\"/> (cùng phụ <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/face0cf4-d5f5-4e02-b2f9-07627ee0114d.png\"/>); <br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/180a320a-a239-4bd3-90d6-3a4063d3ed14.png\"/> (cùng phụ <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/877fcff2-b0ca-464a-b6ae-ce0d1db7dd4f.png\"/>)\n<br>Suy ra  Suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/f2be050c-97d8-402c-b7c2-53b73f05298b.png\"/> (2)\n<br>Mà <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/c26b811c-0f89-49cc-a021-864638767659.png\"/> (3).\n<br>Từ (1), (2) và (3) suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/8d699162-fccc-40a9-9aa2-90ade0a16f35.png\"/>\n<br>Mặt khác <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/fb475ac7-8ea7-4c54-84e3-8ee3660a45d2.png\"/> (AD là phân giác <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/536cd4ae-39c2-4672-b1ee-7a32e0eaa053.png\"/>)\n<br>Suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/9329c1b4-321f-45b4-9ba6-d8e3b4a7bb74.png\"/> suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/22b757ca-dc08-4ec1-b065-064ed7dd3780.png\"/> (đpcm)\n",
